 unloaded its deadweight the vancouver sun financial post retrieved february     french cameron september   barrick boosts equity offering shares slide reuters retrieved february     nystrom scott september   bullish move barrick breaks free from hedges forbescom archived from the original on january   retrieved february     a b bieshuevel thomas february   barrick spinoff to create biggest uk gold miner update  business week bloomberg retrieved july     african barrick gold ipo priced at  pence reuters march   retrieved august     ku daisy crust julie march   african barricks ipo bought up fully in london the star toronto retrieved august     african barrick gold and essar energy to join ftse  june   retrieved august     equinox rejects minmetals april   retrieved april     barrick gold beats minmetals to buy equinox minerals bbc news april   archived from the original on april   retrieved april     barrick gold icsid issues decision in favor of antofagasta plc and barrick in reko diq arbitration proceedings wwwjuniorminingnetworkcom retrieved    barrick gold announces sale of  percent of cerro casale and formation of new partnership with goldcorp wwwjuniorminingnetworkcom retrieved    gilroy annie world’s largest gold producer barrick gold market realist market realist inc retrieved november     barrick gold sells  stake in veladero mine to shandong gold for us million wwwjuniorminingnetworkcom retrieved    barrick gold sells  stake in veladero mine to shandong gold for us million forms working group to explore jointdevelopment of pascualama deposit wwwjuniorminingnetworkcom retrieved    barrick gold and novagold approve  million drill program for donlin project alaska wwwjuniorminingnetworkcom retrieved    wright lisa may   barrick takes rare loss on hit to unwind hedge antimine activists arrested outside annual meeting of shareholders toronto star   corpwatch  barrick gold mine transforms pacific island retrieved december     jantzi research – alerts  business  