 pacific railway ltd falling  percent to c toronto dominion bank was among the biggest drags on the index down  percent at c while royal bank of canada also slipped off  percent at c the financials group which accounts for about  percent of the indexs weighting slipped  percent consumerrelated shares added to the general weakness on the toronto market including grocer loblaw which declined  percent to c and pharmacy chain alimentation couchetard which slipped  percent to c additional reporting by leah schnurr editing by w simon and diane craft by alastair sharp  latest news on gold adjantofagasta production rises costs in line with expectations djcopper prices jump on strong chinese economic data  tsx falls weighed by barrick and other gold miners djnewcrest mining  lihir offsets fall in newcrest gold production djacacia mining earnings output fall on tanzania goldconcentrate export ban djmaterials shares fall gold reverses losses  materials roundup  canadian miner sabina gets project goahead shares jump  percent djgold gains as senate drops healthcare bill djmetals  gold prices rise on us inflation data djmetals  gold prices rise on us inflation data more news chart gold duration  auto  months  months  months  months  year  years  years  years max period  day week fullscreen chart technical analysis trends gold short termmidtermlong termtrendsneutralneutralneutral technical analysis traderscom marketsnewsanalysisstock picksportfoliosscreenerswatchliststop  floptoolsour servicesabout surperformance sascontact usadvertiselegal informationsabout usstay connected facebooktwitterpartners b�rse aktien kurse und nachrichtenbest tweets copyright �  surperformance all rights reserved slave tanzania magufuli tells barrick gold corporation  honour your pledge or lose mines  allafricacom english en français my account allafrica by allafrica news sources media kit countries all countries algeriaangolabeninbotswanaburkina fasoburundicamerooncape verdecentral african republicchad